% Facts
disease(diabetes).
disease(hypertension).
disease(obesity).

diet(diabetes, 'Low sugar, high fiber diet with whole grains.').
diet(hypertension, 'Low salt, potassium-rich food and leafy greens.').
diet(obesity, 'Low-calorie, high-protein and fiber-rich food.').

% Rule
suggest_diet(Disease, Diet) :- disease(Disease), diet(Disease, Diet).
